{"article_id":"TS54ha3Lvti4dkMf","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"A few days before the Iowa caucuses , Ted Cruz called Marco Rubio a \" Republican Obama. \"","depth":3},{"id":1,"text":"It was intended to be an insult .","depth":4},{"id":2,"text":"Rubio should take it as a compliment .","depth":4},{"id":3,"text":"Like Barack Obama eight years ago , Rubio is a young and handsome first-term U.S. senator , an eloquent speaker with a compelling personal story","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"who is a candidate for the presidency of the United States .","depth":5},{"id":5,"text":"And like Obama eight years ago , Rubio is in a horse race .","depth":5},{"id":6,"text":"And","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"despite his stumble in Saturday night ' s debate in New Hampshire ,","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"he nonetheless is sitting comfortably behind the leaders","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"and ready to make his move .","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"Once he sees his opening ,","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"he could sprint all the way to the White House .","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"In many ways , America is back","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"where it was eight years ago .","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"Voters are looking for renewed hope and a sense of identity ,","depth":6},{"id":15,"text":"and they want their country to regain its pride and stature in the world .","depth":6},{"id":16,"text":"There is a current of anger in the campaigns of Cruz , Donald Trump and Bernie Sanders ,","depth":5},{"id":17,"text":"but strip away the veneer","depth":6},{"id":18,"text":"and you find an undercurrent","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"that has always driven America :","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"optimism for a better future and for a leader","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"who will represent the dignity , the decorum and the exceptional qualities of the greatest nation in the world .","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"I ' ve had the opportunity","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"to get to know Marco Rubio .","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"I ' ve lived in Miami ,","depth":6},{"id":25,"text":"so I understand his roots and the people","depth":6},{"id":26,"text":"he represents .","depth":6},{"id":27,"text":"I have no doubt","depth":6},{"id":28,"text":"that he can be a great president","depth":6},{"id":29,"text":"- but first he has to win the race .","depth":5},{"id":30,"text":"I ' m a big fan of thoroughbred racing ,","depth":6},{"id":31,"text":"and I ' ve always been fascinated by the sport ' s great champions .","depth":6},{"id":32,"text":"There have been horses like Secretariat and Ruffian","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"who charged out of the gate ,","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"took the lead","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"and never looked back .","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"And there have been others like Seabiscuit ,","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"who stuck comfortably to his pace a few lengths back","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"and then charged out of the pack","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"to win .","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"In this horse race , Rubio is like Seabiscuit .","depth":7},{"id":41,"text":"He ' s in third place right now ,","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"but the leaders","depth":11},{"id":43,"text":"- Cruz and Trump -","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"are well within his sights .","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"And he knows","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"that the winner isn ' t the candidate","depth":11},{"id":47,"text":"who jumps into the lead .","depth":11},{"id":48,"text":"It ' s the one","depth":11},{"id":49,"text":"who finishes first at the national convention .","depth":11},{"id":50,"text":"For Rubio , winning the Republican nomination could be as easy as 3-2-1 :","depth":5},{"id":51,"text":"Finish third in Iowa , second in New Hampshire and first in South Carolina ,","depth":7},{"id":52,"text":"then keep the pedal to the metal all the way to Cleveland .","depth":7},{"id":53,"text":"And","depth":7},{"id":54,"text":"if his performance in Saturday ' s debate lands him lower than second in New Hampshire ,","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"he has more than enough time","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"to get back his stride","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"and overtake the leaders .","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"With that in mind , there are a number of things","depth":6},{"id":59,"text":"that Rubio and his team need to emphasize","depth":6},{"id":60,"text":"as the race kicks into high gear :","depth":5},{"id":61,"text":"This is not the America of 200 years ago .","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"We are the sons and daughters of immigrants from everywhere in the world ,","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"and as the son of Cuban-Americans , Rubio knows this as well as anyone .","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"His parents ' struggle and his rags-to-riches story should be an inspiration to all ethnic groups , not just Latinos ,","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"much as President Obama ' s was eight years ago .","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"Rubio is smart to appeal to the religious Right ,","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"and reaffirming his faiths and beliefs is commendable .","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"But going forward , he ' d be wise to address the equality of all ethnic groups and religions in our country .","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"One of the things","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"Cruz did well in Iowa","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"was to invest in the infrastructure and resources","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"needed to compile big data","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"that could be analyzed","depth":11},{"id":74,"text":"to give his campaign direction .","depth":11},{"id":75,"text":"It mirrored a tactic","depth":9},{"id":76,"text":"that Obama mastered in 2008 ,","depth":9},{"id":77,"text":"and nobody has ever done it better .","depth":8},{"id":78,"text":"Super PACs are great at buying advertising time ,","depth":7},{"id":79,"text":"but they should play an equally important role","depth":8},{"id":80,"text":"in making sure","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"Rubio has the best data-crunching capabilities available .","depth":9},{"id":82,"text":"Rubio finished third in Iowa , behind Cruz and Trump , but closer to Trump","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"than anyone expected .","depth":10},{"id":84,"text":"Now he hopes to finish second in New Hampshire Tuesday , behind Trump ,","depth":12},{"id":85,"text":"who is the heavy favorite ,","depth":12},{"id":86,"text":"and ahead of Cruz .","depth":11},{"id":87,"text":"That could give him the momentum","depth":12},{"id":88,"text":"to come in first on Feb. 23 in Nevada ,","depth":13},{"id":89,"text":"where he ' s been endorsed by Sheldon Adelson ' s powerful Las Vegas-Review ,","depth":13},{"id":90,"text":"and then on Feb. 27 in South Carolina ,","depth":12},{"id":91,"text":"where several key members of his team","depth":14},{"id":92,"text":"- including Terry Sullivan , the director of his PAC , Reclaim America -","depth":14},{"id":93,"text":"have powerful roots .","depth":13},{"id":94,"text":"Just three days later , on March 1","depth":11},{"id":95,"text":"- Super Tuesday -","depth":11},{"id":96,"text":"when voters in 14 states go to the polls ,","depth":10},{"id":97,"text":"he could already be in the lead .","depth":9},{"id":98,"text":"Rubio has been articulate","depth":10},{"id":99,"text":"in laying out how he would deal with issues like immigration , health care and national security ,","depth":10},{"id":100,"text":"and he ' s provided more substantive details on his website than any of his opponents .","depth":9},{"id":101,"text":"Cruz has given him a lot of flak for his involvement with the \" Gang of Eight , \"","depth":11},{"id":102,"text":"but when did seeking bipartisan support","depth":13},{"id":103,"text":"to solve a problem","depth":13},{"id":104,"text":"become a bad thing ?","depth":12},{"id":105,"text":"Rubio should use that to his advantage ,","depth":11},{"id":106,"text":"because working with both parties","depth":13},{"id":107,"text":"to find solutions","depth":13},{"id":108,"text":"is the mark of a great president .","depth":12},{"id":109,"text":"Rubio is one of the best communicators in politics today ,","depth":10},{"id":110,"text":"and he has the ability","depth":12},{"id":111,"text":"to explain his positions clearly ,","depth":12},{"id":112,"text":"providing details on how to improve our health care system ,","depth":12},{"id":113,"text":"protect our country ,","depth":13},{"id":114,"text":"defeat ISIS","depth":15},{"id":115,"text":"and stop illegal immigration","depth":15},{"id":116,"text":"without alienating legal immigrants .","depth":14},{"id":117,"text":"Marco Rubio is a compassionate , brilliant , articulate , focused leader","depth":5},{"id":118,"text":"who can rally America to a new era .","depth":5},{"id":119,"text":"Now is his time","depth":5},{"id":120,"text":"to sharpen his focus ,","depth":6},{"id":121,"text":"take the lead at the end of the first turn ,","depth":7},{"id":122,"text":"pace himself in the backstretch","depth":9},{"id":123,"text":"and leave the others in his dust","depth":9},{"id":124,"text":"as he sprints to the finish line .","depth":8}],"relations":[{"parent":249,"left":146,"right":248,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":146,"left":127,"right":145,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":127,"left":0,"right":126,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":126,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":145,"left":135,"right":144,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":135,"left":128,"right":134,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":128,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":134,"left":5,"right":133,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":133,"left":131,"right":132,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":131,"left":6,"right":130,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":130,"left":7,"right":129,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":129,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"